to keep alive the contra struggle against the leftist government of 
nicaragua 
the account a legal admission of fact read to the jury with 
the agreement of the prosecution said bush personally told the 
president of honduras in 1985 that extra aid was being funneled to 
his country as payment for helping the contras 
