walesa declared for the first time we have talked to each 
other using the force of arguments and not the arguments of force 
grazyna staniszewska a member of the unions national executive 
committee delivered a powerful plea to poles to take advantage of 
the chance to make a democracy of the soviet blocs most 
politically liberal country 
